<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reset Your Password</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: auto;
        }
        h2 {
            color: #333;
        }
        p {
            color: #555;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #007bff;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #f0f0f0;
            display: inline-block;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>Reset Your Password</h2>
        <p>Use the OTP below to reset your password. This OTP is valid for **10 minutes**.</p>
        <div class="otp"><%= otp %></div>
        <p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
        <p class="footer">Security Notice: Never share your OTP with anyone, including our support team.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
